<plot>Paper Heart is a playfully dark fairy tale about a young girl who finds a damaged heart in the forest. After taking it back to her small cottage, she enlists the help of a local inventor and nurses it back to health. The film tells a story of perseverance and imagination that celebrates the richness and beauty of any innovation powerful enough to preserve life and love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422492</url></doc>
